xtension\">Extension</a></code></dt>\n\n<dd><p>The editor theme styles for One Dark.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt id=\"user-content-onedarkhighlightstyle\">\n  <code><strong><a href=\"#user-content-onedarkhighlightstyle\">oneDarkHighlightStyle</a></strong>: <a href=\"https://codemirror.net/docs/ref#language.HighlightStyle\">HighlightStyle</a></code></dt>\n\n<dd><p>The highlighting style for code in the One Dark theme.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt id=\"user-content-color\">\n  <code><strong><a href=\"#user-content-color\">color</a></strong>: {chalky: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, coral: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, cyan: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, invalid: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, ivory: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, stone: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, malibu: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, sage: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, whiskey: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, violet: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, darkBackground: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, highlightBackground: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\">string</a>, background: <a href=\"